        <Parent_String>broadswords [300037050], swords by form [300037049], swords [300037048], edged weapons [300036973], armaments [300420324], weapons [300036926], Weapons and Ammunition (hierarchy name) [300036743], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
